room_title: Escape room "Big Top Murders (Circus of the Damned)" by Xscape Factor in Fayetteville
room_description: Welcome to the Circus of the Damned, where your life is no longer your own! You and your friends have been taken hostage by a demented serial killer who is framing you for a murder you did not commit. You have only sixty minutes to attempt to find the evidence which has been planted. Find them before your time runs out or our serial killer adds another name to his list of victims as you find yourselves facing the death penalty for atrocities you never dreamed possible.
